    dc:description "FIGURES 1–8. Hoplothrips species. H. hongruiae sp. n. 1–5: (1) Head & pronotum; (2) Antenna; (3) Male sternite VIII; (4) Pelta & tergites II–III; (5) Prosternum & mesopresternum. (6) H. fungosus prosternites. Antennal segments III–IV 7–8: (7) H. corticis; (8) H. orientalis." ;
